node.text: I wanted to address the controversy re @mellowjohnnys and @austin_police. We’re living in a time where there is so much noise around every topic. These are unprecedented times, and while we may not always get it right, I appreciate everyone who came together at the shop to try to move the discussion forward.

node.text: Some old footage of us testing out gear for the time trial from Grenoble to Chamroussw. Decision was between TT bike, road bike with clip ons, or a hybrid between the two. Ultimately decided on the road bike. Say what you want but we never lacked passion. We lived and breathed the @letourdefrance. This also gives you an insight into the brilliant mind of @johan_bruyneel which was unparalleled in pro cycling. Enjoy!
